  ; are executed on each iteration, with the final #z resulting
  ; from a user-specified splicing together of the real & imaginary
  ; parts from Formulas 1 & 2.
  ; The 3-term polynomial formula option is
  ;   z = ( CoeffA * z^ExponentA ) + ( CoeffB * z^ExponentB ) + ( CoeffC * z^ExponentC ) + constant

